::DarkMouse::

She walked over to the lab.  She poked her head in and spoke softly 
to Megatron.
"I beg your pardon Commander.  But if it will help, I can give her 
another dose of the drug and she will be unable to control herself.  
She will tell you anything you want to know without hesitation." She 
was standing in the doorway.  But she was shaking on the inside but 
not showing it outwardly.
